  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\"><img alt=\"House Hoare 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/50px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/75px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/100px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Ravos Hoare<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Raper</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\"><img alt=\"House Hoare 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/50px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/75px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/100px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nRavos the Raper</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">House Hoare</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bear_Island\" title=\"Bear Island\">Bear Island</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Harrag_Hoare\" title=\"Harrag Hoare\">Harrag Hoare</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Erich_Hoare\" title=\"Erich Hoare\">Erich Hoare</a> <small>(unconfirmed)</small></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Ravos Hoare</b>, known as <b>Ravos the Raper</b>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> was an <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> raider and the son of <a href=\"/index.php/Harrag_Hoare\" title=\"Harrag Hoare\">Harrag Hoare</a>, an <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_King\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Iron King\">Iron King</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ravos_Hoare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ravos ruled <a href=\"/index.php/Bear_Island\" title=\"Bear Island\">Bear Island</a> during the ironborn invasion of the western coast of the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Stark\" title=\"Theon Stark\">Theon Stark</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Winter\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King of Winter\">King of Winter</a>, personally slew Ravos, but ironborn raids continued under Harrag's grandson, <a href=\"/index.php/Erich_Hoare\" title=\"Erich Hoare\">Erich the Eagle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ravos_Hoare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands: The Black Blood.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The North: The Kings of Winter.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404035118\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: fals